-to-many\n- Tournament ΓåÆ Venue: many-to-one\n- Tournament ΓåÆ Match: one-to-many\n- Match ΓåÆ BoardGame: many-to-one\n- Match ΓåÆ TeamA and TeamB: many-to-one\n"},"tool_use_id":"call_a26ogpIapGJQKKLdVcj5ly2K__vscode-1777821618481","cwd":"d:\\Fax\\ASP_NET\\BoardGameLeague"}
